### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts

###

### Get single contact - replace the id with a real one from your database
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts/69ac4a83448364c972d47d89

###

### Create a new contact
POST http://localhost:8080/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Tony",
  "lastName": "Gabito",
  "email": "tony@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "orange",
  "birthday": "1990-01-15"
}

###

### Update a contact - replace the id with a real one
PUT http://localhost:8080/contacts/69ac4a83448364c972d47d89
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Tony",
  "lastName": "Gabito",
  "email": "tony.updated@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "blue",
  "birthday": "1990-01-15"
}

###

### Delete a contact - replace the id with a real one
DELETE http://localhost:8080/contacts/69ac4a83448364c972d47d89